subject: Re: New QuikScript font: QuikScript Geometric
msgSnippet: Thanks for the encouragement! I ve essentially spent a couple of years gradually refining my techniques with FontForge and making new fonts for practice. All
messageBody:
Thanks for the encouragement! I've essentially spent a couple of years gradually refining my techniques with FontForge and making new fonts for practice. All just 'every now and then' in my spare time of course (I'm a uni student).

No problem, I wasn't even aware this old group required post approval. I really should get myself a Reddit account by now, shouldn't I...
